def_cn: 双子宫，双子座（黄道十二宫之一。出生于5月21日至6月20日之间的人属此星座）
def_en: Gemini is one of the twelve signs of the zodiac. Its symbol is a pair of twins. People who are born approximately between 21st May and 20th June come under this sign.

def_cn: 出生于双子宫时段的人
def_en: A Gemini is a person whose sign of the zodiac is Gemini.
